      {
        title: 'Customizable Content Generation',
        description:
          'Rewrite and transform PAA data into unique, optimized content. Tailor it to match your brand’s voice and style, saving time while making your content more engaging and relevant.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Content Structuring Options',
        description:
          'Use PAA questions to create structured, informative layouts that enhance user engagement. Integrate these questions as subheadings or supporting sections, providing a rich experience for your audience.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Responsive for High SEO Impact',
        description: `The PAA Content Tool ensures your SEO efforts are effective across all devices, maximizing visibility and delivering consistent performance for mobile and desktop users alike.`,
      },
    ]}
    image={{
      src: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1611462985358-60d3498e0364?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2070&q=80',
      alt: 'Astronauts Image',
    }}
  >
    <Fragment slot="content">Empower Your Content Strategy with User-Centric Insights.</Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="bg">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-transparent"></div>
    </Fragment>
  </Content>

  <!-- Steps Widget ****************** -->

  <Steps
    title="Create SEO-Driven Content with OnPage.ai in Just a Few Steps."
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Step 1: <span class="font-medium">Capture and Organize Ideas</span>',
        description:
          "Use the Webdraft Tool to clip and organize content snippets, notes, and ideas from across the web. Create a well-rounded view of your target topic, ideal for content curation and planning.",
        icon: 'tabler:package',
      },
      {
        title: 'Step 2: <span class="font-medium">Generate PAA-Based Content</span>',
        description:
          "Scrape “People Also Ask” (PAA) questions from Google using the PAA Content Tool. Rewrite and customize these insights to target long-tail keywords, enrich your content, and match user search intent.",
        icon: 'tabler:letter-case',
      },
      {
        title: 'Step 3: <span class="font-medium">Build Topic Clusters</span>',
        description:
          'Visualize and organize content into clusters using the Topic Clustering Tool. Generate a mindmap of related topics, helping you structure content around key themes for stronger SEO impact.',
        icon: 'tabler:paint',
      },
      {
        title: 'Ready!',
        icon: 'tabler:check',
      },
    ]}
    image={{
      src: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1616198814651-e71f960c3180?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=987&q=80',
      alt: 'Steps image',
    }}
  />

  <!-- HighlightedPosts Widget ******* -->

  <BlogLatestPosts
    title="Find out more content in our Blog"
    information={`The blog serves as a hub for OnPage.ai resources and guides. Each article is designed to enhance your expertise in SEO and content optimization, helping you make the most of OnPage.ai’s powerful tools. Stay tuned for insights, tips, and best practices to elevate your SEO strategy.
                `}
  />

  <!-- FAQs Widget ******************* -->

  <FAQs
    title="Frequently Asked Questions"
    subtitle="Dive into the following questions to gain insights into the powerful features that AstroWind offers and how it can elevate your web development journey."
    tagline="FAQs"
    classes={{ container: 'max-w-6xl' }}
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Was OnPage.ai previously known as SimilarContent.com, and can old AppSumo LTD customers still use the new extension?',
        description:
          "Absolutely yes! Previous LTD customers from AppSumo still have full access to OnPage.ai. Plus, as a thank you for your loyalty, we’ve sent an extra gift to your email. If you’ve been an AppSumo client since 2020, please check your inbox to find our special offer!",
      },
      {
        title: 'What is OnPage.ai, and how can it help my SEO?',
        description:
          'OnPage.ai is a comprehensive Chrome extension designed to simplify SEO analysis, content curation, and topic clustering. It helps you understand competitor strategies, optimize on-page elements, and create content that aligns with user search intent.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Do I need any special requirements to install OnPage.ai?',
        description:
          "Yes, to fully utilize OnPage.ai, you'll need: A licensed email associated with your OnPage.ai account, An OpenAI API key for AI-driven features, Access to our server developer API. Once set up, you can perform unlimited analyses, topic clustering, and PAA content generation using the extension.",
